profile: Stanton Excavation has been a family run business for over 39 years. What began as Ivan Stanton Excavation has since been renamed to  Stanton Excavating and Backhoe Service. We specialize in lot clearing, demolition, dirt removal, excavation and grading, foundations, landscaping, site preparation, substation site development, septic preparation, lot grading, debris removal, concrete breaking and hauling, foundations. Call us today for your next project.
